Interface Worker


  • public interface Worker
    Interface of worker objects. All Methods in Worker that implement MapCommand & CommandChain annotations.

    Note: Client should be aware of Server side <command::function> set. (type and number of arguments and return object of each function/command)

    Author:
    Yaser Eftekhari ( ^ - ^ )
    See Also:
    MapCommand, CommandChain
